{"id":476918,"date":[{"year":1966,"month":6,"day":30}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"工农兵纪念“七一”诗画选,歌唱共产党　歌唱毛主席","genre":"","count":"149","ytitle":"","mtitle":"誓作革命促进派","ftitle":"","authors":["邱学胜"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"驻沪空军某部学员　邱学胜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心头装满恨和爱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"握紧枪杆拿笔杆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"口诛笔伐斗黑线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昂首持枪意志坚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们深恨黑帮“三家村”；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热爱世界人民在心怀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁教我懂得恨和爱?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"主席著作随身带。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“阶级”二字心上刻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"突出政治传万代，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五洲四海眼底收，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"誓作革命促进派。"}]}